item.title: Cheerful Loving Couple Bakers Drinking Coffee
item.description: Myself, Chris Price, James Black, Tad Lewandoswki, Harper Forbes & Kiran Bonda represented Roche/Genentech at the recent PHUSE US Connect in Atlanta. We presented a wide range of topics between us covering the pharmaverse, NEST, admiral, learnings from open source collaborations, leadership in an agile world, and automation in analysis results development.
